<h3>Rated: <%=movie.Rated%></h3>
<h3>Runtime: <%=movie.Runtime%></h3>
<h3>Genre: <%=movie.Genre%></h3>
<h3>Director: <%=movie.Director%></h3>
<h3>Writer: <%=movie.Writer%></h3>
<h3>Metascore: <%=movie.Metascore%></h3>
<h3>BoxOffice: <%=movie.BoxOffice%></h3>
